        "subject": "LU-5934 mdt: faulty assertion in mdt_intent_reint",
        "message": "LU-5934 mdt: faulty assertion in mdt_intent_reint\n\nmdt_intent_reint() may set lhc::mlh_reg_lh for resent request,\nwhich means lhc::mlh_reg_lh can be a valid lock handle when\nprocessing of resent request failed.\n\nThis patch also includes code cleanup for mdt_object_open_lock\nand mdt_object_open_unlock\n\nSigned-off-by: Liang Zhen <liang.zhen@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I665892c90586f4f0663204d380e279a7d2e8ac8d\n"
      },
